# Job Alert Bot (Cursor)

## What this repo is

A Node.js **ESM** Discord bot that aggregates UK jobs from **25** sources, scores and filters them (relevance, **RAG**, seniority, salary), enriches descriptions and extracts structured fields, stores everything in **SQLite**, posts alerts to Discord, and optionally serves a separate **dashboard** (analytics, charts, run logs, applied/discarded actions).

## Sources

Adzuna, Reed, Serper, LinkedIn, Jooble, Careerjet, Guardian Jobs, JobServe, Construction Enquirer, CV-Library, Rise Technical, CIOB Jobs, BIM+ Jobs, Technojobs, Totaljobs, CWJobs, Hays, Michael Page, Matchtech, Morson, Advance TRS, ICE Recruit, Monster, Glassdoor (`src/sources/*.js`, plus `stepstone_platform.js`, `next_data_extract.js`, `browser.js`). Prefer fixing shared logic under `src/utils/` rather than duplicating per adapter.

## Important paths

- **Bot & pipeline:** `src/index.js`, `src/config.js`, `src/db.js`, `src/discord.js`
- **Schema / migrations:** `src/jobs-schema.js` (must stay safe for both writer and dashboard)
- **Scoring & filtering:** `src/utils/rag.js`, `src/utils/seniority.js`, `src/utils/salary.js`, `src/utils/relevance.js`, `src/utils/search.js`
- **Enrichment:** `src/utils/enrich.js`, `src/utils/extractors.js`
- **Dashboard:** `src/dashboard.js`, `src/dashboard/server.js`, `src/dashboard/data-access.js`, `src/dashboard/aggregate.js`, `src/dashboard/public/`
- **Searches:** `data/searches.json` (reloaded each run; keep aligned with `src/config.js` normalization)

## Commands

- `npm start` — bot
- `npm run once` — single run
- `npm run dashboard` — dashboard (default port **3099**)
- `npm run check` — syntax check across bot + dashboard modules
- `npm test` — tests
- `npm run backfill:extractors` — backfill extraction columns

## Dashboard env (when not on localhost)

Set `DASHBOARD_TOKEN` if `DASHBOARD_HOST` is not loopback. Optional reverse-proxy prefix: `DASHBOARD_BASE_PATH`.

## Conventions

- Do not break the full fetch cycle when one source fails.
- After schema changes, update `src/jobs-schema.js` and any affected inserts/queries/tests.
- Full project reference: see `CLAUDE.md` in the repo root.
